	<Title>
		Fibromyalgia treatment: Is Neurontin effective?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Fibromyalgia treatment &amp;mdash; Gabapentin may be effective, but studies are limited.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is gabapentin (Neurontin, others) an effective fibromyalgia treatment?
	</Question>
